Depaulitte, Appellant, v. Depaulitte, Appellee.

[Cite as Depaulitte v. Depaulitte (2001), 91 Ohio St.3d 1201.]

(No. 00-470 Submitted December 13, 2000 Decided January 31, 2001.)

The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

*1202David R. Schmidt, for appellant Jacqueline J. Depaulitte. Donenfeld, Botros, Kollin & Schulte and Richard W. Schulte, for appellee Brian E. Depaulitte. Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
